messages.speaker: therapist
messages.text: Hi! I'm Anita Bhargava. Strategic wealth building with modern perspective. I'm here to help you understand your financial lifestyle and goals. To get started, could you please tell me your name?

messages.speaker: therapist
messages.text: Namaste Anika! I'm delighted to meet someone at such an exciting stage of life. At 22, you're at the perfect moment to start building a strong financial foundation. Let's explore your financial journey together. To understand your lifestyle better, could you tell me about three key aspects of your life: where you currently live and what type of housing arrangement you have, how you typically spend your weekdays, and what activities bring you joy in your free time?

notes.note: Young professional/recent graduate, age indicates early career stage
